[l] BBC-Interview mit Ted Malloch. Der Mann ist angeblich Trumps Wunschkandidat als EU-Botschafter.Der Interviewer fragt:Why do you want to be ambassador to the EU? I mean you clearly are not a great friend of Brussels, its bureaucrats like Jean-Claude Juncker?Daraufhin grinst Malloch in die Kamera und erklaert:Well, I had in a previous career a diplomatic post where I helped bring down the Soviets. So maybe this is another union that needs a little taming.Holla!
